env PAGER=cat man timing_constraint_load_minimal_set_for_automated _eco
Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
timing_constra..._automated_eco(25.10)  timing_constra..._automated_eco(25.10)

Name
       timing_constraint_load_minimal_set_for_automated_eco

Syntax
       timing_constraint_load_minimal_set_for_automated_eco {true | false}

       Default: false

       Skips  loading the SDC constraints that are not required, when the sig-
       noffOptDesign command is used. The timing data is obtained from the ECO
       timing database - this global variable reduces the TAT for designs with
       complex constraint mode files.

       To set this global variable, use the set command.

